00:46:32.720 --> 00:46:47.698
When we all see Jesus, we'll sing and shout the victory. Thank you, Lord.

00:46:47.699 --> 00:47:00.879
You're coming so soon. Oh, hallelujah! Every knee will bow and every tongue will confess that Jesus is Lord.

00:47:00.880 --> 00:47:09.683
Every knee will bow. It's going to be wonderful, and a thousand-year reign.

