01:02:39.597 --> 01:02:50.056
Or wherever, and you're going, 'Where are we at?'We just got off course just a little bit, and the next thing you know, over a course of time, we're in Cuba and we're supposed to be in Jacksonville.

01:02:50.057 --> 01:02:56.203
