01:03:14.193 --> 01:03:20.496
And I said, 'I don't know who that was for, but I was supposed to say it.'And I pray it blessed you.

01:03:20.497 --> 01:03:26.732
But I felt in my heart the Lord said to say that part of it. Well, I think that's good enough for today.

01:03:26.733 --> 01:03:30.552
I pray this video blessed y'all. I really do. Diana and I love you.

01:03:30.553 --> 01:03:35.705
We pray for you all the time. Thank you for joining us. Let's pray a little prayer.

