01:08:19.078 --> 01:08:24.420
Freely we've been given, freely we give it out, folks. And we are just here to tell you Jesus loves you and he's coming back soon.

01:08:24.421 --> 01:08:30.713
Thank you for helping us. That's all we ask. All these people saying they're asking for—what is it?

01:08:30.714 --> 01:08:34.317
What do they call—you said you got how many scammers this week?

01:08:34.318 --> 01:08:38.147
Impersonators. Yeah, there's a lot of impersonators. It's been a lot today.

01:08:38.148 --> 01:08:44.699
Yeah, we never, ever will private message anyone. We're not on WhatsApp, we're not on Telegram.

01:08:44.700 --> 01:08:54.308
And there's people on YouTube that use our profile picture and they'll find ways. What is the new thing today, though, is why I'm saying that.

01:08:54.309 --> 01:09:01.452
They said they call it the family channel, 'The Family of the Last Days'or something.

01:09:01.453 --> 01:09:07.515
It's some stupid account, and I told them, I said, 'That's—'and they're asking, 'Family of the Last Days'is asking you to give them money.

01:09:07.516 --> 01:09:13.961
That is not me. And I had people screenshot it and send me pictures, and it's been more than one, though, several people.

01:09:13.962 --> 01:09:19.908
So just know that we're not on WhatsApp, we never will be, and we're not on Telegram, and we never will be.

01:09:19.909 --> 01:09:26.461
And we will never, ever, ever message you or ask you for anything. I do not give financial advice. No.

01:09:26.462 --> 01:09:30.266
Anything I ever say is my opinion, and that's not for you ever to do.

01:09:30.267 --> 01:09:32.871
These people are trying to tell you to invest in stuff; that's not me.

01:09:32.872 --> 01:09:38.808
And as soon as we go after them and ban them, they just create a new one.

01:09:38.809 --> 01:09:44.977
It's like the saying goes: if the devil can't get you, he'll keep you busy.

01:09:44.978 --> 01:09:48.469
That's exactly what it feels like; we're always trying to put out the fires.

01:09:48.470 --> 01:09:55.540
I told her, 'We just don't have time to do it anymore.'So just be aware of that, and if you see them, report them and just know that it's not us.

01:09:55.541 --> 01:09:58.852
All of our social media links are always in the description below.

01:09:58.853 --> 01:10:03.283
If you don't find the social media link in that description, it's not us.

01:10:03.284 --> 01:10:08.963
People will also go on Facebook, Instagram, and TikTok, and they'll create accounts and impersonate us over there, too.

01:10:08.964 --> 01:10:15.044
So just be aware that if it's not here directly on this channel, make sure this is the correct YouTube channel.

01:10:15.045 --> 01:10:25.988
If you see it in the description, that's us. We always have verification checkmarks.

01:10:25.989 --> 01:10:33.194
We just want to love on y'all and tell y'all, 'God bless y'all.'Remember, put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

01:10:33.195 --> 01:10:42.239
Jesus loves you so much, and we love you. God bless you all, and we'll see you again soon. Bye-bye.

